{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"double","preciseIdentifier":"c:d","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tileLodZoomShift","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Shift applied to the Zoom level during LOD calculation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A negative value shifts the Zoom level to a coarser level reducing quality but improving","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"performance A positive value shifts the Zoom level to a finer level increasing details but","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"negatively affecting performance A value of zero (default) does not apply any shift to the Zoom","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"level It is not recommended to change the default value unless performance is critical and the loss","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of quality is acceptable. A value of -1 reduces the number of displayed tiles by a factor of 4 on","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"average It is recommended to first configure the pixelRatio before adjusting TileLodZoomShift.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/tileLodZoomShift"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"tileLodZoomShift","